<section id="experience" aria-labelledby="experience-label">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" id="experience-label">Track Record</p>
    <div class="exp-list">
      {jobs.map((job) => (
        <article class="exp-item">
          <div class="exp-date">{job.date}</div>
          <div class="exp-content">
            <h3>{job.title}</h3>
            <div class="exp-company">{job.company}</div>
            <div class="exp-headline">{job.headline}</div>
            <p>{job.description}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
      <div class="exp-earlier">
        <strong>Earlier career (2006–2020):</strong> Development Team Lead at Be.Live (real-time multi-participant streaming with WebRTC), Senior Dev → Tech Lead → Solutions Lead at Thomas Cook (three promotions in three years, shaped multi-market travel platform frontend architecture), Development Team Lead at Astound Commerce (managed teams up to 20 engineers, built e-commerce reference applications), JavaScript Tech Lead at SmartBear Software, Demandware Developer at R3 Systems Group, and systems engineering at PortaOne and PrivatBank.
